Executive Summary

Company Overview

PartsSource is a leading provider of mission-critical healthcare equipment parts, services, and intelligence. A 10-person services team currently manages $120M in annual renewals across 4,000+ accounts in the REMI portfolio. This initiative focuses on the long-tail segment (policies under $20k)  approximately 1,500 accounts representing ~$20M in ARR  where structured, proactive renewal engagement does not currently exist.

 

