Section 5: Communication and Customer Engagement

Agent Configuration

Languages

English is assumed as the primary language based on the US-focused customer base confirmed on March 9. Please confirm whether any customers require communication in other languages.

 

Agent Personality and Voice

The agent should reflect the relationship-oriented, consultative tone the PartsSource customer service team uses today. The team emphasized the value of “consistent messaging” with the to sound like a trusted, knowledgeable team member, not a generic automated system. Brad described the aspiration as replicating the experience the account management team provides, at a scale that wasn’t previously possible.

 

Email Templates



Standard: Remi Renewal Notification – [Account Name] – [Policy Number] effective [Start Date]

When changes exist: Remi Renewal Coverage Change Notification – [Account Name] – [Policy Number] effective [Start Date]

Expired: Remi Expired Coverage Notification – [Account Name] – [Policy Number] expired [Date]



Template 1: Initial Outreach (T-180)

Subject: [Customize together]

Hi [First_Name],

[Opening that reflects your brand voice and existing relationship  acknowledge the upcoming renewal naturally]

[Value paragraph referencing their specific service history or outcomes where available]

[Clear call-to-action appropriate to the T-180 stage  sentiment check, any equipment changes anticipated]

[Signature]

 

Template 2: Follow-Up  Engaged Customers

[Variations based on customer health signals and prior engagement  to be built with Renewal Queen templates as reference]

 

Template 3: Follow-Up  At-Risk or Non-Responsive Customers

[More consultative approach for customers showing disengagement signals or service delivery concerns]

 

Template 4: Renewal Delivery (T-60 PO-based / T-30 auto-renew)

[Formal renewal agreement delivery  based on existing Renewal Queen templates for price increases, vendor changes, and standard renewals]

 

Phone Scripts

Voice outreach scope: TBD  confirm whether voice is in scope for the REMI segment in Phase 1. Taylor confirmed sub-$20k renewals are resolved via email “more often than not.” Voice may be Phase 2.

 

